name: Traditional House #4 - Bangsal Kencono
description: It's a pixel sprite 120x120 upscale to 1200x1200 of traditional house from Special Region of Yogyakarta, Indonesia. Bangsal Kencono (Bangsal Kencana) is traditional house of Mataram Sultanate that still used at Keraton Yogyakarta (The Palace of Yogyakarta).
